response: Salary sacrificing is an arrangement where your employer makes contributions into your super before tax is deducted from your salary. This may reduce your income for tax purposes. Complete a request form and give it to your payroll officer or HR department. To download a form and for more information, visit: visionsuper.com.au. Select "Super" from the top menu and then "Grow my super" on the left. Anything else I can help you with?
